window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>Cultivate Magic Mushrooms in the Comfort of Your Home</i></p> <p><b>Are you....</b></p> <p></p> <ul> <li>interested in alternative healing methods?</li> <li>looking for culinary inspiration?</li> <li>eager to cultivate healing mushrooms?</li> </ul> <p><b>Then read on! </b></p> <p>Mushrooms have been a part of traditional medicine in many cultures. Healing mushrooms were especially well known in China and Mesoamerica.&nbsp;</p> <p>In the United States, research into magic mushrooms was curbed by increasingly strict drug laws - even though psilocybin, a substance naturally occurring in many mushrooms, has been proven to improve mental health in people with depression and&nbsp;PTSD, it was declared an illegal drug. This is why magic mushrooms can’t be a part of mainstream medicine.&nbsp;</p> <p><i>However, you can cultivate magic mushrooms by yourself.</i> Don’t worry if you don’t have gardening skills or experience - mushrooms are not plants and their cultivation is different from normal gardening. All you need is the knowledge you’ll find in this book.&nbsp;</p> <p>This introduction to growing magic mushrooms explains everything in a beginner-friendly way so you'll avoid mistakes and successfully cultivate magic mushrooms to heal your mind. Of course, you can also use the techniques described here to grow any mushrooms you like - many are delicious and have numerous health benefits.&nbsp;</p> <p><i>Here’s what you’ll find in this book: </i></p> <p></p> <ul> <li>A detailed step-by-step instruction to planting mushrooms and taking care of them</li> <li>Culinary tips and recipes with mushrooms&nbsp;</li> <li>A guide to the medical benefits of mushrooms&nbsp;</li> <li>Step-by-step strategies to use mushrooms for weight loss, blood sugar management, and other medical purposes</li> <li>And much more!</li> </ul> <p>It’s true that mushrooms can be dangerous if you’re not sure which species you’re consuming. However, the knowledge you’ll find in this book will help you avoid poisonous mushrooms and only cultivate the good ones!&nbsp;</p> <p><b><i>Grow your own magic mushrooms even if you’ve never grown anything before! </i></b></p> <p>Scroll up, click on \"buy now\", and get your copy now!</p>"; 
